### Meeting Management API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Create Meeting Place
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meeting-places
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "قاعة الاجتماعات الرئيسية",
  "type": 0,
  "location": "الطابق الأول",
  "capacity": 20,
  "contactInfoJson": "{\"phone\":\"+966-11-123-4567\"}"
}

### 2. Get All Meeting Places
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meeting-places
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. Create Meeting
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "اجتماع إدارة المشروع",
  "agenda": "مناقشة تقدم المشروع والتخطيط للمرحلة القادمة",
  "type": 0,
  "locationMode": 0,
  "startAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00",
  "endAt": "2024-01-15T11:30:00",
  "placeId": 1,
  "attendees": [
    {
      "kind": 0,
      "userId": "user1",
      "role": 0,
      "notes": "مدير المشروع"
    },
    {
      "kind": 1,
      "displayName": "أحمد محمد",
      "organization": "شركة التقنية",
      "email": "ahmed@tech.com",
      "role": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Get All Meetings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings?search=اجتماع&type=0&status=0&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31&pageSize=10&pageNumber=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Get Meeting by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Update Meeting
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "اجتماع إدارة المشروع - محدث",
  "agenda": "مناقشة تقدم المشروع والتخطيط للمرحلة القادمة - محدث",
  "type": 0,
  "locationMode": 0,
  "startAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00",
  "endAt": "2024-01-15T11:30:00",
  "placeId": 1
}

### 7. Update Meeting Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

### 8. Get Meeting Attendees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meetings/1/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Add Attendee to Meeting
